The paper is about public opinion of artificial intelligence, which falls under the category of AI. The survey also covers concerns about privacy and job loss, which could be categorized under CY (computers and society). The mention of healthcare applications suggests a possible connection to HC (human-computer interaction). The identification of different sentiments in different countries could be related to SI (social and information networks) or SY (systems and control).
